<html>
  <head>
    <title>The Gossip Project</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;">

    <h1>Bienvenue sur ce super site de potins !</h1>
    <h2>Cr√©ation d'un nouveau potin</h2>
    <span>Pour ajouter ton potin, clique donc <a href="/gossips/new/"><button style="background:#FF7F50;color:white;border-radius:5px;">ici</button></a> !</span>
    </br>
    <h2>Liste des potins existants</h2>
      <table style="border: 1px solid black;font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:10px;">
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
          <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:2px;background:#008080;color:white;text-align:center;"><strong>Gossip IDs</strong></td>
          <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:2px;background:#008080;color:white;text-align:center;"><strong>Authors</strong></td>
          <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:2px;background:#008080;color:white;text-align:center;"><strong>Contents</strong></td>
          <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:2px;background:#008080;color:white;text-align:center;">Update</td>
          <td style="border: 1px solid black;padding:2px;background:#008080;color:white;text-align:center;">Delete</td>
        </tr>
        <% 
          tmp_line = 1
          gossips.each do |gossip| 
            if tmp_line % 2 == 0 
              tmp_color = "#AFEEEE"
            else
              tmp_color = "#E0FFFF"
            end
            tmp_line += 1
        %>
        <tr style="border: 0px;">
          <td style="background:<%=tmp_color%>;border: 1px dotted black;padding:2px;text-align:center;"><a href="/gossips/<%=gossip.id.to_s%>"><strong><%=gossip.id.to_s%></strong></a></td>
          <td style="background:<%=tmp_color%>;border: 1px dotted black;padding:2px;"><%=gossip.author%></td>
          <td style="background:<%=tmp_color%>;border: 1px dotted black;padding:2px;"><%=gossip.content%></td>
          <td style="background:<%=tmp_color%>;border: 1px dotted black;padding:2px;"><a href="/gossips/edit/<%=gossip.id.to_s%>"><button style="background:#2E8B57;color:white;border-radius:5px;">Update</button></a></td>
          <td style="background:<%=tmp_color%>;border: 1px dotted black;padding:2px;"><a href="/gossips/delete/<%=gossip.id.to_s%>"><button style="background:#B22222;color:white;border-radius:5px;">Delete</button></a></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
      </table>

  </body>
</html>